description:
Darling, Darling, Darling. There is truth to the
statement that a painter is only as good as the
quality of the paint he is working with. Same holds
true to Riggers. They are only as good as the models
they are working with. Darling is a true BDSM
lifestyler, who loves bondage almost more than
anything in her life. Some of Hogtied's best imagery
comes when Matt and Darling get together. Enjoy.
title: Darling
